ster drone flight using your Meta Quest controllers for a natural and responsive piloting experience.\n- **Realistic Flight Physics**: Experience authentic drone behavior with accurate physics simulation, providing a genuine sense of flight.\n- **Immersive Audio**: Hear the buzz of propellers and the rush of wind, adding a new dimension to your virtual flight experience.\n- **Freeform Exploration**: Enjoy the freedom to fly wherever you want without constraints or objectives - the sky's the limit!\n- **VR Optimization**: Enjoy smooth performance and crisp visuals optimized for the Meta Quest platform, ensuring a comfortable and engaging experience.\n\n---\n\n**Drone Experience** offers an accessible yet realistic drone flying experience in VR. Whether you're an aspiring drone pilot or simply curious about the sensation of flight, this app provides a unique opportunity to soar through virtual skies.\n\nNo missions, no stress - just pure, unadulterated flight. \n\n> Take to the skies and experience the thrill of drone piloting in VR today!", "short_description": "Experience the freedom of drone flight in virtual reality. Control a drone with intuitive VR controls and immerse yourself in a realistic flying experience with authentic sounds."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.ravit.dev/privacy-policy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.ravit.dev/terms-and-conditions/", "publisher_name": "Ravit Dev", "support_website_url": "https://www.ravit.dev/", "website_url": "https://www.ravit.dev/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "388572352490011"}, {"id": "331529188132278"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_pro